<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>MyAnime (Rails)</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 2rem; background: #f6f7fb; color: #111827; }
      .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; max-width: 820px; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(17,24,39,.08); }
      code { background: #eef2ff; padding: .15rem .35rem; border-radius: 6px; }
      li { margin: .45rem 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>MyAnime</h1>
      <p>React + Spring Boot 구성을 Ruby on Rails 단일 앱으로 전환한 상태입니다.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>헬스체크: <code>GET /api/health</code></li>
        <li>인증: <code>POST /api/auth/register</code>, <code>POST /api/auth/login</code>, <code>GET /api/auth/me</code></li>
        <li>도메인 API: <code>/api/anime</code>, <code>/api/news</code>, <code>/api/quotes</code>, <code>/api/anime/:id/like</code></li>
        <li>인제스트: <code>POST /api/admin/ingest/all</code> 및 provider별 엔드포인트</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
